<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Privacy Policy - Jain Parichay Biodata Group</title>
    <link
      rel="stylesheet"
      href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css"
    />
    <link
      href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto,
          "Helvetica Neue", Arial, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #333;
      }

      .privacy-container {
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 4rem 0;
      }

      .privacy-section {
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
      }

      .privacy-section h2 {
        color: #0066cc;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        font-size: 1.5rem;
      }

      .privacy-section h3 {
        color: #444;
        margin: 1.5rem 0 1rem;
        font-size: 1.2rem;
      }

      .privacy-section p {
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
      }

      .privacy-section ul {
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        padding-left: 1.5rem;
      }

      .privacy-section li {
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      }

      .back-to-home {
        position: fixed;
        bottom: 20px;
        right: 20px;
        z-index: 1000;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="privacy-container">
      <h1 class="text-center mb-5">Privacy Policy</h1>

      <div class="privacy-section">
        <h2>1. Introduction</h2>
        <p>
          At Jain Parichay Biodata Group, we take your privacy seriously. This
          Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your personal
          information when you use our service.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="privacy-section">
        <h2>2. Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>We collect the following types of information:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>
            Personal information from your biodata (name, age, birth year,
            education, etc.)
          </li>
          <li>Contact information (phone number, email, address)</li>
          <li>Family background information</li>
          <li>Professional and educational details</li>
          <li>Preferences for potential matches</li>
          <li>Communication history with us</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="privacy-section">
        <h2>3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <p>We use your information for the following purposes:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>
            Sharing your biodata with potential matches based on birth year
          </li>
          <li>Communicating with you about potential matches</li>
          <li>Providing updates about our service</li>
          <li>Improving our matching service</li>
          <li>Ensuring the security of our platform</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="privacy-section">
        <h2>4. Information Sharing</h2>
        <p>We share your information only in the following circumstances:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>With potential matches based on birth year and preferences</li>
          <li>With community members for family parichay purposes</li>
          <li>When required by law or legal process</li>
          <li>With your explicit consent</li>
        </ul>
        <p>We never sell or rent your personal information to third parties.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="privacy-section">
        <h2>5. Data Security</h2>
        <p>
          We implement appropriate security measures to protect your
          information:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Secure storage of biodata information</li>
          <li>Limited access to personal data</li>
          <li>Regular security assessments</li>
          <li>Encrypted data transmission</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="privacy-section">
        <h2>6. Your Rights</h2>
        <p>You have the right to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Access your personal information</li>
          <li>Correct inaccurate information</li>
          <li>Request deletion of your information</li>
          <li>Opt-out of communications</li>
          <li>Withdraw consent at any time</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="privacy-section">
        <h2>7. Data Retention</h2>
        <p>
          We retain your information only for as long as necessary to provide
          our service or as required by law. You can request the deletion of
          your information at any time.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="privacy-section">
        <h2>8. Changes to Privacy Policy</h2>
        <p>
          We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify
          you of any significant changes through our platform or via email.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="privacy-section">
        <h2>9. Contact Us</h2>
        <p>
          If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy or our data
          practices, please contact us through WhatsApp.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Back to Home Button -->
    <a href="/" class="btn btn-primary back-to-home">
      <i class="fas fa-home me-2"></i>Back to Home
    </a>

